['Diary of a Wimpy Kid', 6.8, '2021-12-03', 1406.529, 'Greg Heffley is a scrawny but ambitious kid with an active imagination and big plans to be rich and famous – he just has to survive middle school first.', 'Fantasy'],
['No Time to Die', 7.5, '2021-09-29', 1284.626, 'Bond has left active service and is enjoying a tranquil life in Jamaica. His peace is short-lived when his old friend Felix Leiter from the CIA turns up asking for help. The mission to rescue a kidnapped scientist turns out to be far more treacherous than expected, leading Bond onto the trail of a mysterious villain armed with dangerous new technology.', 'Fantasy'],
