['Venom: Let There Be Carnage', 7.2, '2021-09-30', 7992.617, 'After finding a host body in investigative reporter Eddie Brock, the alien symbiote must face a new enemy, Carnage, the alter ego of serial killer Cletus Kasady.', 'History'],
['Red Notice', 6.8, '2021-11-04', 3496.837, "An Interpol-issued Red Notice is a global alert to hunt and capture the world's most wanted. But when a daring heist brings together the FBI's top profiler and two rival criminals, there's no telling what will happen.", 'History'],
